snippet.title: NU: Carnival - Bliss Brand-New Animated Opening Released
snippet.description:
We thank every Master for their unceasing support. It's because of you that the Klein continent has become such a dazzling place and that every character could be made to shine. 💫

Please continue to keep Eiden, the clan members, and the familiars company in what may follow, and join them on happy adventures on the Klein continent to create even more beautiful memories~ 💝

Observant Masters have probably noticed... that the accompanying background music seems to be... 👀✨

#ニューブリ #NUCarnival_Bliss
